divs: Sighting DetailsWhile driving, two men noticed two black triangular objects (each side 40-50feet) hovering 300-350 feet away. A white light was at each point and ared-orange light was centered underneath. At each rear point was a protrusionextending a few feet beyond the rear side. No sound was heard. The witnessesexited their car to observe. The objects soon rotated, then glided slowly away.Duration of the sighting was estimated as 25 minutes.
